msgid ""
"---\n"
"title: How to use Sudachi dictionary for synonym expansion\n"
"---"
msgstr ""
"---\n"
"title: 同義語展開にSudachiの辞書を使う方法\n"
"---"

msgid "## How to use Sudachi dictionary for synonym expansion"
msgstr "## 同義語展開にSudachiの辞書を使う方法"

msgid ""
"[SudachiDict][sudachi-dict] provides a synonym dictionary. We can use it in "
"PGroonga."
msgstr ""
"[SudachiDict][sudachi-dict]は同義語辞書を提供しています。PGroongaでこれを使う"
"ことができます。"

msgid ""
"We explain how to use the synonym dictionary in SudachiDict in your search "
"system. We use the synonym dictionary in SudachiDict as the system "
"dictionary here. We can use additional synonym dictionary defined by us."
msgstr ""
"検索システムでSudachiDictにある同義語辞書を使う方法を説明します。ここでは"
"SudachiDictにある同義語辞書をシステム辞書として使います。さらに自分たちで定義"
"した同義語辞書も使います。"

msgid "### How to register contents of the synonym dictionary in SudachiDict"
msgstr "### SudachiDictにある同義語辞書の内容を登録する方法"

msgid ""
"We need to create a table for system synonym dictionary based on "
"SudachiDict. We name it `system_thesaurus` here:"
msgstr ""
"SudachiDictベースのシステム同義語辞書のためのテーブルを作る必要があります。こ"
"こではこのテーブルの名前は`system_thesaurus`にします。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"CREATE TABLE system_thesaurus (\n"
"  term text PRIMARY KEY,\n"
"  synonyms text[]\n"
");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"We need a PGroonga index to use it as synonym dictionary. It must use "
"`pgroonga_text_term_search_ops_v2` operator class for `term` that is used as "
"synonym key:"
msgstr ""
"このテーブルを同義語辞書として使うにはPGroongaのインデックスが必要です。この"
"インデックスでは、同義語のキーとして使う`term`の演算子クラスに"
"`pgroonga_text_term_search_ops_v2`を指定しなければいけません。\n"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"CREATE INDEX system_thesaurus_term_index\n"
"  ON system_thesaurus\n"
"  USING pgroonga (term pgroonga_text_term_search_ops_v2);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"We can use [Groonga synonym][groonga-synonym] to register contents of the "
"synonym dictionary in SudachiDict to `system_thesaurus`."
msgstr ""
"SudachiDictにある同義語辞書の中身を`system_thesaurus`に登録するために"
"[Groonga synonym][groonga-synonym]を使います。"

msgid "Groonga synonym is written in Ruby. We need to install Ruby at first."
msgstr ""
"Groonga synonymはRubyで書かれています。そのため、事前にRubyをインストールして"
"おかないといけません。"

msgid "Install Groonga synonym:"
msgstr "Groonga synonymをインストールします。"

msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"gem install groonga-synonym\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The following command line generates `INSERT` to register contents of the "
"synonym dictionary in SudachiDict to `system_thesaurus`:"
msgstr ""
"次のコマンドラインはSudachiDictにある同義語辞書の内容を`system_thesaurus`に登"
"録する`INSERT`を生成します。"

msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"groonga-synonym-generate --format=pgroonga --table=system_thesaurus --"
"output=system_thesaurus_data.sql\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The generated data has weight because SudachiDict provides relation "
"information."
msgstr ""
"SudachiDictが関連情報を提供しているので生成されたデータには重みがついていま"
"す。"

msgid "We can load the data by `\\i` in `psql`:"
msgstr "このデータは`psql`内で`\\i`を使ってロードできます。"

msgid ""
"```text\n"
"\\i system_thesaurus_data.sql\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "### How to register user synonym dictionary"
msgstr "### ユーザー同義語辞書の登録方法"

msgid ""
"We need to create a table for user synonym dictionary. We use [synonym "
"groups usage][pgroonga-query-expand-usage-synonym-groups] here. Because "
"maintaining synonym dictionary is high cost task. Synonym groups usage is "
"less maintenance cost than [term to synonyms usage][pgroonga-query-expand-"
"usage-term-to-synonyms]."
msgstr ""
"ユーザー同義語辞書用のテーブルを作る必要があります。ここでは[同義語グループ]"
"[pgroonga-query-expand-usage-synonym-groups]を使います。なぜなら同義語辞書の"
"メンテナンスはコストが高いタスクだからです。同義語グループの方が[単語ごとに同"
"義語を指定する][pgroonga-query-expand-usage-term-to-synonyms]よりもメンテナン"
"スコストが低いです。"

msgid "We name it `user_synonym_groups` here:"
msgstr "ここではこのテーブルの名前を`user_synonym_groups`にします。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"CREATE TABLE user_synonym_groups (\n"
"  synonyms text[]\n"
");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"We need a PGroonga index to use it as synonym dictionary. It must use "
"`pgroonga_text_array_term_search_ops_v2` operator class for `synonyms` that "
"is used as synonym group:"
msgstr ""
"このテーブルを同義語辞書として使うためにはPGroongaのインデックスが必要です。"
"同義語グループとして使われる`synonyms`には"
"`pgroonga_text_array_term_search_ops_v2`演算子クラスを指定する必要がありま"
"す。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"CREATE INDEX user_synonym_groups_synonyms_index\n"
"          ON user_synonym_groups\n"
"       USING pgroonga (synonyms pgroonga_text_array_term_search_ops_v2);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "Here are sample data:"
msgstr "以下はサンプルデータです。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"INSERT INTO user_synonym_groups VALUES (ARRAY['pg', 'postgresql']);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"We can get the same search result for `pg` and `postgresql` with this "
"synonym groups data. If we search with `pg`, `pg OR postgresql` is used as "
"query. If we search with `postgresql`, `pg OR postgresql` is used as query."
msgstr ""
"この同義語グループデータを使うと、`pg`で検索しても`postgresql`で検索しても同"
"じ検索結果になります。`pg`で検索するとクエリーは`pg OR postgresql`になりま"
"す。`postgresql`で検索してもクエリーは`pg OR postgresql`になります。"

msgid "### How to search with synonym dictionaries"
msgstr "### 同義語辞書を使った検索方法"

msgid ""
"We can use [`pgroonga_query_expand` function][pgroonga-query-expand] twice "
"to search with synonym dictionaries."
msgstr ""
"これらの同義語辞書を使って検索するために[`pgroonga_query_expand`関数]"
"[pgroonga-query-expand]を2回使います。"

msgid "First `pgroonga_query_expand()` uses user synonym dictionary:"
msgstr "最初の`pgroonga_query_expand()`はユーザー同義語辞書を使います。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT\n"
"  pgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"    'user_synonym_groups',\n"
"    'synonyms',\n"
"    'synonyms',\n"
"    'QUERY'\n"
"  );\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "Here is an example to use `pg` as query:"
msgstr "クエリーに`pg`を使った場合の例です。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT\n"
"  pgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"    'user_synonym_groups',\n"
"    'synonyms',\n"
"    'synonyms',\n"
"    'pg'\n"
"  );\n"
"--  pgroonga_query_expand  \n"
"-- ------------------------\n"
"--  ((pg) OR (postgresql))\n"
"-- (1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "Both of `pg` and `postgresql` will be searched."
msgstr "`pg`も`postgresql`も検索されます。"

msgid ""
"Second `pgroonga_query_expand()` uses system synonym dictionary against the "
"result of the first `pgroonga_query_expand()`:"
msgstr ""
"2つめの`pgroonga_query_expand()`は1つめの`pgroonga_query_expand()`の結果に対"
"してシステム同義語辞書を使います。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT\n"
"  pgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"    'system_thesaurus',\n"
"    'term',\n"
"    'synonyms',\n"
"    pgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"      'user_synonym_groups',\n"
"      'synonyms',\n"
"      'synonyms',\n"
"      'QUERY'\n"
"    )\n"
"  );\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "We add one more synonym group to the user synonym dictionary:"
msgstr "ユーザー同義語辞書にもうひとつ同義語グループを追加します。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"INSERT INTO user_synonym_groups VALUES (ARRAY['on-line', 'online']);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "Let's confirm the new synonym group:"
msgstr "新しく追加した同義語グループを確認しましょう。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT\n"
"  pgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"    'user_synonym_groups',\n"
"    'synonyms',\n"
"    'synonyms',\n"
"    'on-line'\n"
"  );\n"
"--   pgroonga_query_expand  \n"
"-- -------------------------\n"
"--  ((on-line) OR (online))\n"
"-- (1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Let's use both system synonym dictionary and user synonym dictionary with "
"`on-line` as query:"
msgstr ""
"クエリーに`on-line`を指定してシステム同義語辞書とユーザー同義語辞書を両方使っ"
"てみましょう。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT\n"
"  pgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"    'system_thesaurus',\n"
"    'term',\n"
"    'synonyms',\n"
"\tpgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"      'user_synonym_groups',\n"
"      'synonyms',\n"
"      'synonyms',\n"
"      'on-line'\n"
"    )\n"
"  );\n"
"--               pgroonga_query_expand               \n"
"-- --------------------------------------------------\n"
"--  ((on-line) OR (((>-0.2オンライン) OR (online))))\n"
"-- (1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "Here is the workflow of the above `SELECT`:"
msgstr "この`SELECT`は次のように動きます。"

msgid ""
"  1. `on-line` is expanded to `on-line OR online` with user synonym "
"dictionary: `on-line` -> `((on-line)) OR (online))`"
msgstr ""
"  1. `on-line`はユーザー同義語辞書で`on-line OR online`に展開されます：`on-"
"line` -> `((on-line)) OR (online))`"

msgid ""
"  2. `online` is expanded to `>-0.2オンライン OR online` with system synonym "
"dictionary: `((on-line)) OR (online))` -> `((on-line) OR (((>-0.2オンライン) "
"OR (online))))`"
msgstr ""
"  2. `online`はシステム同義語辞書で`>-0.2オンライン OR online`に展開されま"
"す：`((on-line)) OR (online))` -> `((on-line) OR (((>-0.2オンライン) OR "
"(online))))`"

msgid ""
"Note that `>-0.2` in `>-0.2オンライン` adjusts weight for `オンライン`. It "
"uses `0.8` (`1 - 0.2`) as weight."
msgstr ""
"`>-0.2オンライン`の`>-0.2`は`オンライン`の重みを調整しています。この場合、重"
"みは`0.8` (`1 - 0.2`)になります。"

msgid "Let's use the synonym dictionaries with full text search:"
msgstr "全文検索でこれらの同義語辞書を使ってみましょう。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"CREATE TABLE memos (\n"
"  content text\n"
");\n"
"INSERT INTO memos VALUES ('Online conference is easy to join');\n"
"INSERT INTO memos VALUES ('On-line conference is easy to join');\n"
"INSERT INTO memos VALUES ('オンライン conference is easy to join');"
msgstr ""

msgid "CREATE INDEX memos_content_index ON memos USING pgroonga (content);"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"-- For ensuring using index\n"
"SET enable_seqscan = no;"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"SELECT content, pgroonga_score(tableoid, ctid) AS score\n"
"  FROM memos\n"
"  WHERE\n"
"    content &@~\n"
"      pgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"        'system_thesaurus',\n"
"        'term',\n"
"        'synonyms',\n"
"        pgroonga_query_expand(\n"
"          'user_synonym_groups',\n"
"          'synonyms',\n"
"          'synonyms',\n"
"          'on-line'\n"
"        )\n"
"      );\n"
"--                content                |       score       \n"
"-- ---------------------------------------+-------------------\n"
"--  On-line conference is easy to join    |                 1\n"
"--  オンライン conference is easy to join | 0.800000011920929\n"
"--  Online conference is easy to join     |                 1\n"
"-- (3 rows)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

